            <lg xml:id="TK1242">
<l>kāta lavarila rākanī nōvatu </l>
<l> pētaimai vāḻiyeṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May you live, O my soul! While he is without love, for you to suffer is (simple) folly.</l>
